CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1958, pg. 3 reads: "3. Popular deejay, Bill Powell, acted as M.C. for some very wonderful, crowd-pleasing entertainment."
TitMainTitle: Crowd of people in front of MC Bill Powell, standing in demonstration kitchen with Daisy Lampkin and Jessie Vann in background, for the 1958 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair in Syria Mosque
